      <p class="text-sm sm:text-lg text-[#111] max-w-xl mx-auto md:mx-0 text-center md:text-left">You’ve bootstrapped and delivered an MVP, and some investors and advisors are interested in having a chat with you. With TangleCat, you can onboard them seamlessly into your digital organization and align them with your success.</p>
    </div>
